  "id": "RAW_7c6d6a",
  "title": "今日开源（2025-03-03）：HumanOmni，7B 全方位多模态大模型，专注人物场景理解，动态融合面部、身体与交互信息",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/50vrSG8MIcXL8mmCGfYXBg",
  "date": "2025-03-03 10:13:19",
  "author": "每日发现最新LLM",
  "siteName": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <section class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 0px;\">\n   <mp-common-profile class=\"custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe mp_common_widget\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-id=\"MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/GU2ibjU7TDkyqTqr59u8fKegUibXxHSW3WF3ib6u8lQO8JicgNbPzicmhb8kPjrkYk6libDSD7ia1RlxQN9bWugwjguOg/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-nickname=\"机器之心SOTA模型\" data-alias=\"sotaai\" data-signature=\"追踪 AI 开源进展，探索先进开发实践。\" data-from=\"0\"></mp-common-profile>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><strong><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap-style: initial;\"><strong style=\"font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(58, 60, 70);letter-spacing:0.51px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.51px;\">①项目：HumanOmni</strong></span></strong></strong></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"100014113\" data-ratio=\"0.4810281517747858\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"817\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ea300248-e4d9-4509-cbca-6d159558b100/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ea300248-e4d9-4509-cbca-6d159558b100/public\"></p>\n  <p><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(58, 60, 70);letter-spacing:0.51px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:start;\">★HumanOmni是业界首个人物中心的全方位多模态大语言模型，旨在对人物中心场景进行全面理解。</span></strong><span style=\"color:rgb(58, 60, 70);letter-spacing:0.51px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:start;\">该项目构建了一个包含超过240万个人物中心视频片段的数据集，并提供了超过1400万条视觉预训练指令数据。此外，</span><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(58, 60, 70);letter-spacing:0.51px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:start;\">还手动标注了5万个视频片段，包含超过10万条与情感识别、面部描述和特定说话人语音识别相关的指令，用于视觉微调和跨模态</span><span style=\"color:rgb(58, 60, 70);letter-spacing:0.51px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:start;\">交互集成</span></strong><span style=\"color:rgb(58, 60, 70);letter-spacing:0.51px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:start;\">。HumanOmni通过三个分支分别处理与面部、身体和交互相关的场景，并能动态调整融合权重，以确保在各种场景中提供准确的响应。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">☆一键收藏：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/humanomni</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><strong><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap-style: initial;\"><strong style=\"font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(58, 60, 70);letter-spacing:0.51px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.51px;\"><br></strong></span></strong></strong></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><strong><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap-style: initial;\"><strong style=\"font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(58, 60, 70);letter-spacing:0.51px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.51px;\">②项目：Spark-TTS</strong></span></strong></strong></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"619\" data-imgfileid=\"100014110\" data-ratio=\"0.9951768488745981\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"622\" data-width=\"622\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fe700e6a-55ae-4865-729d-3c6fc2280300/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fe700e6a-55ae-4865-729d-3c6fc2280300/public\"></p>\n  <p><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(58, 60, 70);letter-spacing:0.51px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:start;\">★Spark-TTS 是一个先进的文本转语音系统，利用大语言模型（LLM）的强大功能，实现高度准确和自然的语音合成。</span></strong><span style=\"color:rgb(58, 60, 70);letter-spacing:0.51px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:start;\">该项目旨在为研究和生产提供高效、灵活和强大的语音合成解决方案。其特点包括简化的生成过程、高质量的语音克隆、双语支持以及可控的语音生成。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">☆一键收藏：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/spark-tts</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><br></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️框架平台、必备工具</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><strong><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap-style: initial;\"><strong style=\"font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(58, 60, 70);letter-spacing:0.51px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.51px;\">①项目：DexGraspVLA</strong></span></strong></strong></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"100014114\" data-ratio=\"0.6214549938347719\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"811\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a11bce44-db05-4573-b1cc-7bbfa1461a00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a11bce44-db05-4573-b1cc-7bbfa1461a00/public\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color:rgb(58, 60, 70);letter-spacing:0.51px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:start;\">★<strong>DexGraspVLA是一个分层的视觉-语言-动作框架，在复杂场景中实现了90%以上的灵巧抓取成功率</strong>，即使面对成千上万种未见过的物体、光照和背景组合，也能在“零样本”真实环境中表现出色<strong>。该框架能够完成需要复杂视觉语言推理的长时间抓取任务。</strong>其关键在于利用预训练的视觉语言模型作为高层任务规划器，并通过扩散式模仿学习获取灵巧动作。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">☆一键收藏：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/dexgraspvla</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><strong><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap-style: initial;\"><strong style=\"font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(58, 60, 70);letter-spacing:0.51px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.51px;\"><br></strong></span></strong></strong></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><strong><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap-style: initial;\"><strong style=\"font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(58, 60, 70);letter-spacing:0.51px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.51px;\">②项目：AReaL</strong></span></strong></strong></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"445\" data-imgfileid=\"100014109\" data-ratio=\"0.5514250309789344\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"807\" data-width=\"807\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8fd1bb4b-5e1b-43df-2aae-4b1cff71a300/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8fd1bb4b-5e1b-43df-2aae-4b1cff71a300/public\"></p>\n  <p><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(58, 60, 70);letter-spacing:0.51px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:start;\">★AReaL是一个开源且高效的强化学习系统，由Ant Research的RL实验室开发。</span></strong><span style=\"color:rgb(58, 60, 70);letter-spacing:0.51px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:start;\">该项目继承并改进了开源项目ReaLHF，用于训练大规模推理模型（LRMs），以便所有人都能复现和贡献。AReaL是Ant Research为构建一个完全开放和包容的AGI世界而开发的工具和系统的一部分。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">☆一键收藏：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/areal</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><strong><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap-style: initial;\"><strong style=\"font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(58, 60, 70);letter-spacing:0.51px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.51px;\"><br></strong></span></strong></strong></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><strong><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap-style: initial;\"><strong style=\"font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(58, 60, 70);letter-spacing:0.51px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.51px;\">③项目：SepLLM</strong></span></strong></strong></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"375\" data-imgfileid=\"100014108\" data-ratio=\"0.4606879606879607\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"814\" data-width=\"814\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7773925a-89de-40e6-da28-dbf0e1e17e00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7773925a-89de-40e6-da28-dbf0e1e17e00/public\"></p>\n  <p><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(58, 60, 70);letter-spacing:0.51px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:start;\">★SepLLM 是一个旨在加速大型语言模型推理的框架。</span></strong><span style=\"color:rgb(58, 60, 70);letter-spacing:0.51px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:start;\">通过将某些分隔符标记的段落信息压缩到分隔符标记中，SepLLM 能够在不显著损失信息的情况下减少冗余标记，从而提高推理速度。此外，<strong>项目还实现了高效的训练加速内核。</strong>实验结果表明，SepLLM 在多种训练设置下均表现出色，尤其是在使用 Llama-3-8B 骨干时，在 GSM8K-CoT 基准测试中实现了超过 50% 的 KV 缓存减少，同时保持了可比的性能。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">☆一键收藏：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/sepllm</span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><strong><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap-style: initial;\"><strong style=\"font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(58, 60, 70);letter-spacing:0.51px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.51px;\"><br></strong></span></strong></strong></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><strong><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap-style: initial;\"><strong style=\"font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(58, 60, 70);letter-spacing:0.51px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neu